----------------------------------------------------------------------

Portions of this product are derived from DecoKee's DecoKeeAI / DK-Suite
project (Copyright DecoKee / MatrixZero), used under the Apache License,
Version 2.0:

  - Glyph icon assets (Quake4Mac/Icons/)
  - Video wallpaper assets (Quake4Mac/Wallpapers/)
